    "faq": {
      "type": "faq",
      "blocks": {
        "faq_1": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How does the aira nasal strip work?",
            "answer": "<p>Two small adhesive tabs sit just above your nostrils. The magnetic strip connects them and gently lifts your airway open. Nothing inside your nose, no drugs, and the hold at 6am is the hold at 11pm.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_2": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Is it comfortable to sleep with, and what if it falls off?",
            "answer": "<p>The strip weighs less than 2 grams, and most people forget it's on within minutes. The medical-grade tabs hold all night and peel off clean. Either way, the 30-night guarantee covers you.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_3": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "How long does the strip last?",
            "answer": "<p>The strip is reusable and built to last. You only replace the adhesive tabs: 1 pair per night, in packs from 30 to 360 pairs.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_4": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Will it help with my snoring?",
            "answer": "<p>Most snoring is mouth breathing. Open the nose and you switch back to nasal breathing, which quiets the vibration behind the noise. Partners usually notice before you do.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_5": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Can I use it during exercise?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes, this is where aira shines. The tabs are sweat-proof and hold through hard sessions and Gulf heat. In one study, runners needed 22% less air for the same pace (Dallam et al., 2018).</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_6": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question": "Do you ship to the GCC?",
            "answer": "<p>Yes. Free shipping in the UAE, arriving within 3 to 5 business days.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
